answers.answer: I'm sorry I wish I could help. I have a problem with tension headaches. I'm 38 weeks as well the Dr told me if I get a headache and I start seeing spots or Tylenol doesn't dull or Take away the pain to go to the hospital because I have had high blood pressure my last few visits it could be a sign of preeclampsia. I don't say this to scare you or anything just wanted to share what I was told
